data.description: STOP THE CAR!!!!  MOVE IN ASAP!  Looking for a new home but do not want to wait for it to be built, Here it is.....This 2023 home is located in the highly desirable gated community of Thompson Preserve and will not disappoint.  Additionally, the home is covered by Builder's home warranty. Located in a USDA Eligible area,  buyer's can receive 100% Financing.    This home has a split bedroom floor plan that features immaculate finishes, boasting generously sized guest rooms, master suite with walk-in closet, upgraded flooring, PVC Vinyl fenced rear yard, large open concept, high ceilings, and rear patio. Thompson Preserve community is conveniently located near downtown Bartow and is an short distance from Earnest Smith Blvd and the upcoming 700 acre Stuart Crossing, with a wide range of medical, bike trails, green spaces, shops and restaurants that will make Stuart Crossing one of Polk County’s most desirable places to live, work and visit. Stuart Crossing represents the future of Bartow’s continued growth. This home is move in ready and sellers can close and transition timely.
